#This file shows how one might like
#to set a wiimote to control one's media

#first, lets change player 1 to simulate a keyboard
change 1 keyboardmouse

#These buttons are sensible in all the mappings:
assign wiimote plus key_volumeup
assign wiimote minus key_volumedown
assign nunchuk plus key_volumeup
assign nunchuk minus key_volumedown
assign classic plus key_volumeup
assign classic minus key_volumedown

#lets hold the wiimote vertically, like a remote.

assign wiimote a key_playpause
assign wiimote b key_mute
assign wiimote left key_previous
assign wiimote right key_next
assign wiimote home key_stop
assign wiimote 1 key_shuffle
assign wiimote up key_brightnessup
assign wiimote down key_brightnessdown
